Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～好漂亮的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:00:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩也是一年级的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小京  不要吓我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  咲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么事  小京
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校食堂吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
