Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给…女生套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  居然就为了这餐把我拉来食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天的女生用餐实在是好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小京真会使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻将？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小京  你打麻将的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才刚记住全部的役就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻将真是有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…讨厌麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？咲  你会打麻将吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是会…但是我讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直和家里人打麻将  总是输
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲干什么都不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总比少个人要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便陪陪我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不够的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人…不够？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻将部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旧校舍的楼顶有部门活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  小京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎  公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找了个冤大头来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小京  我都说了我讨厌麻将了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么怎么  你认识和吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  刚才在桥附近读书的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被看到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然互相认识那就好说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和是去年的全国中学生大会的优胜者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很厉害么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:03:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在学校餐厅买了墨西哥饼喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是墨西哥饼么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会拿你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去倒茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和真的很厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在去年的全国中学生大会获得优胜的最强中学生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且父母是检事与律师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很受男生们欢迎喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和某人大不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在里面睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就我们几个来下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没说要下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是呢…那开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初始点25000  计分点30000  没有顺位加减得点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥饼真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  和家人以外的人打还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点和！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混一色  2000点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常会点炮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不很容易就看出在做筒子么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是初学者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～立直啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我点和了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你舍弃三色三同顺想怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外行人也该有个限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福  我是第一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也是自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是和第一名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～进入下一局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  咲的麻将真是不怎么出彩啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点数倒像是会计算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打雷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下起雨来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没带伞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我中学时的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫宫永咲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是竹井久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个学校我不是学生会长而是学生议会长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是麻将部的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上的牌不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断幺九 平和 三色三同顺  最少也有7700点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是和第一名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  宫永咲  就是她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1000点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1000点？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汇报点数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸九万  扔掉六万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要故意去掉断幺九与三色三同顺来降低点数呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九万也不是危险牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次也是小和第一名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫永同学的点数是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是正负0点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三回连续正负0点！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先不打了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长醒了人数也凑齐了  我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经要回去了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去图书馆还书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走得很匆忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为小和太强了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压倒性的胜利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压倒性的胜利？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么傻话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着她的点数就没什么注意到的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫永同学的点数是三回连续正负0点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你要说这是故意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能  碰巧的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻将受运气影响很大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专业的也不过第一位确率在30%左右就算很强了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更别说正负0点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比赢还要难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还连续三回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得不可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有压倒性的力量差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和是怎么了  突然跑出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩  能不能进我们部呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那样算上真子就五个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们部  说不定能进军全国哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三回连续正负0点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次我打麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要那么打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是在和家人打麻将时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了的话就拿不到点心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一直赢的话也会被骂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中  就变成这种打法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫永同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再与我打一局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每回打出正负0点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是人类能做到的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不打了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为自己再也不打了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲  洗澡要洗到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一如既往很受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在从早上起就吃便当？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了哦  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似有个每回都以正负0点和的一年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  消息真灵通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  和赢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢是赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自尊方面会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下卷被借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么被借走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学…学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生议会长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么在意小细节啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别偷看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这书我有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全集都有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我借你啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我对宫永同学有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心上人来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须贺同学  把优希叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这样啊  这个文学少女就是那个正负0点的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才发现啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优希  人齐了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  马上去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫永同学  和  真子  还有优希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小咲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这四个人进行二回战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我上的话大家就都没得玩了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真敢说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回是东风战  赤牌四张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这还算是麻将部员么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来解说喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的麻将多为半庄战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从东一局到南四局为止打8局的是主流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而东风战则又是其一半
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从东一局到东四局  只进行四局比赛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  就是说所需时间变为一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有所谓的赤牌是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被涂红的5的牌  赤牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次有四张这样的牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝牌有…8张？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种恐怖的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初始点25000 计分点30000对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了书  约好只下两回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长给了我机会  今天从一开始就要认真去打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲还是要打出正负0点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照一般的想法  每回正负0点是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天还是带赤牌的东风短期决战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看吧  你的真正的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄家  立直  上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二巡  一点也看不透她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不好的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚～立直一发自摸加三张宝牌  庄家跳满！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优希的过去平均获得点数图表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东场是很能挣点数啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是到了南场就会失去势头变弱的类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但集中力无法持续就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易厌烦才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8300点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是染谷学姐扔掉的牌喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1000点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样前进喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优希那家伙  想逃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  情况变的有意思了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听牌么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断幺九平和加两张宝牌  11600点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就连庄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的规则是百位上的点数以五舍六入来算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要达成正负0点的话  点数就要在29600点到30500点之间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸  门前清混一色红中役牌加一张宝牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲家3000  庄家6000  每人再加一本场100分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～我不想听那样长长的咒文了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  本想只是看看情况的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  最后一局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是咲的门前清混一色听牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能点和的话就是5200点  正好正负0点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从优希那里直接拿来的话  就能一举成为第一了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过一巡的赤五筒也不要！？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼中一点也没有胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用优希的五筒来和的话  貌似可以正负0点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那样就会因为第一而追加点数
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用和的赤五筒来和的话  顺位虽然没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却会变成满贯而无法达成正负0点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩除了正负0点什么也不想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫永同学应该是想达成5200点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直棒出来的话  会如何做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真是坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会变成增加1000点对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  这样要达成正负0点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要打出4100点到5000点之间的点数
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  必须是70符2番
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,70符是…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从麻将部的记录来看  70符的出现几率基本是千分之一
